{"tid":1449973,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「改善」集會同遊行期間請大家自發式開個讀書會！唔好浪費時間！","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T03:49:13.000Z","uid":143865,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"56b2e85e64f8be534b2376c2c13a0f0d2d0587c6","tid":1449973,"uid":143865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:13:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔係要搞嘉年華</span><br />\n見好多次大家企出黎都有鳩流流既情況！<br />\n請大家把握咁多香港人出左黎既機會！<br />\n唔好怕醜！自由發揮！<br />\n自發式開組同大家清清concept!<br />\n<br />\n例如討論<br />\n1.點解我地要堅持呢個運動！<br />\n2.運動失敗左，香港點樣陷入絕境<br />\n3.運動兩個月以黎要改善既地方（保護自己既方式，咩裝備最好，咩易容方法最冇手尾跟，進場退場既時機同路線，互相報料既方法，點樣撚狗，etc)<br />\n4.順便幫一直以黎頹左既人打氣"},{"pid":"b072fad6f49a59a08c51ed00396ac04eebfbba1d","tid":1449973,"uid":143865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:15:44.000Z","msg":"仲有討論<br />\n5.被捕後有咩援助，可以點做<br />\n6.普通市民享有咩權利<br />\n7.被截查時可以點保護自己<br />\n8.有咩警例可以撚狗<br />\n9.平時出街見狗行bi可以點撚"},{"pid":"88d8b1787f068bad8779cbc1366b8200358fed02","tid":1449973,"uid":143865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:15:55.000Z","msg":"自推十個"},{"pid":"08c0e4c2d537327dc2badfad0b11486d5c4b8a5e","tid":1449973,"uid":143865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:17:58.000Z","msg":"一"},{"pid":"852d789b8ebf56998e0458569d21bdded59b0314","tid":1449973,"uid":143865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:18:08.000Z","msg":"二"},{"pid":"5334043085548ff5eb1ef4334180aab4c4ec6d17","tid":1449973,"uid":143865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:22:31.000Z","msg":"三"},{"pid":"4ab69382bc2e7a8416dc0336d093df631391b7e8","tid":1449973,"uid":143865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:22:46.000Z","msg":"四"},{"pid":"48e11486b077e0fc48e6cca659136c35ea34cb76","tid":1449973,"uid":143865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:22:57.000Z","msg":"五"},{"